{"tid":1650201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵疑再變運兵車 持盾防暴獨霸觀塘綫旺角一列車","createTime":"2019-10-13T00:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:48:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f94ff4aa118c2c63c7e2f872e4b9b0418eb0050a","tid":1650201,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"抗暴之戰】港鐵疑再變運兵車 持盾防暴獨霸觀塘綫旺角一列車<br />\n <br />\n有網民今午3時再在尖沙嘴舉行「反對緊急法遊行」，抗議蒙面惡法、警方濫暴濫捕等問題。遊行由尖沙嘴鐘樓集合，前往深水埗運動場。期間防暴警進入油麻地港鐵站戒備，部份警員進入車站控制室。網上流傳一段影片，片中大批防暴警現身港鐵觀塘綫旺角站往黃埔方向的一列車車廂內，同時站內廣播輕鐵將不會經過友愛、天榮、銀座、天湖、天慈、天水圍等站。<br />\n<br />\n據網上消息指，港鐵下午曾開出「運兵專列」，下午約4時45分左右，由九龍灣車廠接載一批防暴警到油麻地執勤。防暴警專用列車約下午5時半到達旺角站，被在月台候車的網民拍下全車「清一色」防暴警。根據片段紀錄，當時列車到達旺角站後一度停站，但沒有開門供乘客上落。有當時乘坐觀塘綫列車的網民亦指，觀塘綫服務疑一度受影響，每次到站要停站接近5分鐘才開出。港鐵發言人下午約6時半回覆時僅稱，觀塘綫列車服務「現時」維持正常。<br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見，有防暴警再度進駐太子站戒備，全部警員均戴上口罩，無佩帶委任證。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191012/60146773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60146773&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=9c455855\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60146773&h=c0ff4ea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191012/60146773</a>"},{"pid":"fcc81b8ea2d036b060d4370e115b8b8dc2c4df12","tid":1650201,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:40:49.000Z","msg":"香港有特急坐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b616481b8d40a8816d05b3932e24bfda1d194fd","tid":1650201,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:48:10.000Z","msg":"開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf40e222ffacbb7fbc3a8891e41726924f55de8","tid":1650201,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"召喚泥水同燒焊師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8fd9be12c9893876ba748abdcecfa71c61e5b2","tid":1650201,"uid":48060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:49:36.000Z","msg":"又話運暴徒好難睇既"},{"pid":"96910e5fbc89242f7e0f0c426c00e65b4c6300bc","tid":1650201,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵石屎埋撚咗佢啦"},{"pid":"f7f2de3ad6b9cd2bef453fd5eaa285ef7ca57c8b","tid":1650201,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"當初起高鐵同要直入西九都係想咁"},{"pid":"ed8ec891b69b11ddae4420d7c8abd0e4c061dbae","tid":1650201,"uid":45082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7f2de3ad6b9cd2bef453fd5eaa285ef7ca57c8b","tid":1650201,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"當初起高鐵同要直入西九都係想咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"石崗停車場隔離就係石崗軍營<br />\n果個位又有緊急月台..."},{"pid":"8a4ef8df8b403c908c116cfdf54ded3fd79886c3","tid":1650201,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:35:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4303ffe6a64ea8f5cb0583d57666706b9c11b7e5","tid":1650201,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4655ba78365abcb26044cdf5be162c026b96dda4","tid":1650201,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"下次知運狗<br />\n一定禁停緊急制"}]}